    <w:p><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading2"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>PROFESSIONAL SUMMARY</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    <w:p><w:r><w:t>Results-driven Senior QA Automation Engineer with 12+ years of progressive experience architecting and delivering enterprise-grade test automation solutions across Financial Services, Healthcare, and Insurance sectors. Proven expertise in designing scalable automation frameworks, implementing CI/CD pipelines, and optimizing QA processes to accelerate release velocity while maintaining zero-defect quality standards. Track record of leading cross-functional teams and driving digital transformation initiatives in highly regulated environments.</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:spacing w:line="240"/></w:pPr></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading2"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>CORE COMPETENCIES</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading3"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>Test Automation &amp; Frameworks</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    <w:p><w:r><w:t>Selenium WebDriver | Playwright | Cypress | Cucumber (BDD/TDD/ATDD) | TestNG | JUnit | Page Object Model (POM) | Data-Driven Testing (DDT) | Hybrid Frameworks</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading3"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>API &amp; Services Testing</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    <w:p><w:r><w:t>REST API | SOAP | GraphQL | RestAssured | SoapUI | Postman | Karate DSL | APIGEE</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:pStyle w:val="Heading3"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>Programming Languages &amp; Scripting</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    <w:p><w:r><w:t>Java | JavaScript | TypeScript | Python | Groovy | C# | SQL | Gherkin | JSON | XML | HTML</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
