    <w:p><w:pPr><w:ind w:left="720"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>• Performed end-to-end scenario testing for ACH processing, funds transfer, settlement, and account management workflows, validating complex business rules and reconciliation logic</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:ind w:left="720"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>• Executed functional and regression testing within Agile Scrum environment; collaborated with development and product teams to identify and document defects</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
    <w:p><w:pPr><w:ind w:left="720"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t>• Developed SQL-based backend validation scripts to ensure data integrity across payment transaction flows</w:t></w:r></w:p>
    
